to open up a port for trade/to open treaty ports

sentences.english: Typically, the modem is connected to one of the serial ports on the computer.
sentences.chinese: 一般而言，數據機會連接至電腦上的其中一個序列埠。

sentences.english: By default an available unprivileged port will be chosen at runtime.
sentences.chinese: 預設情況下，在運行時將選擇一個可用的無特權埠。

sentences.english: The console port does not support hardware flow control .
sentences.chinese: 主控臺埠不支援硬體流量控制。

sentences.english: Ask your system administrator what port you should specify.
sentences.chinese: 請洽詢您的系統管理員，瞭解您應該指定的埠。

sentences.english: The main processor and the Ethernet port are located on the Pentium CPU module.
sentences.chinese: 主要處理器和乙太網路埠，位於奔騰CPU模塊。

sentences.english: Clients and servers use ports to distinguish which process each segment is associated with.
sentences.chinese: 客戶端和伺服器使用埠來區分每個區段所結合的程序。

sentences.english: Ports transition from the listening state to the learning state.
sentences.chinese: 埠從傾聽狀態轉換到學習狀態。

sentences.english: Here you should choose the serial port you connect the camera to.
sentences.chinese: 您可以在這裏選擇您照相幾所連結的序列埠位址。

sentences.english: Ports transition from the blocking state to the listening state.
sentences.chinese: 埠從阻隔狀態改變到傾聽狀態。
